ed; line count:\"; wc -l < \"$F\""},"output":"appended; line count:\n       3\n","metadata":{"output":"appended; line count:\n       3\n","exit":0,"truncated":false},"title":"F=\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/mcp-tooling/010-mcp-mobbin/001-research/research/lineages/glm/deep-research-state.jsonl\"\nprintf '%s\\n' '{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"run\":1,\"status\":\"complete\",\"focus\":\"Broad survey of mobbin-mcp-server + mobbin/skills repos\",\"findingsCount\":6,\"newInfoRatio\":1.0,\"noveltyJustification\":\"First broad pass; transport model (remote Streamable HTTP), repo thinness, single mobbin-search skill, image-inline results, and install path are all new to this packet.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"kq1\",\"kq2\",\"kq3\",\"kq5\",\"kq6\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"kq3\",\"kq5\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Read the auth/plan-gating/tool-list from the server repo README\",\"reason\":\"READMEs omit auth, plan gating, and explicit tool names; canonical source is docs.mobbin.com/mcp + server.json\",\"evidence\":\"https://github.com/mobbin/mobbin-mcp-server\"}],\"graphEvents\":[{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-remote-http\",\"label\":\"Transport = remote Streamable HTTP at api.mobbin.com/mcp (no local process)\"},{\"type\":\"finding\",\"id\":\"f-skills-search\",\"label\":\"mobbin/skills defines one design-research skill: mobbin-search\"},{\"type\":\"edge\",\"from\":\"f-skills-search\",\"to\":\"f-remote-http\",\"relation\":\"DEPENDS_ON\"}],\"convergenceSignals\":{\"rollingAvg\":null,\"madScore\":null,\"entropyCoverage\":0.33,\"compositeStop\":0.0,\"note\":\"1 evidence iteration; rolling/MAD unavailable; stopPolicy=max-iterations so convergence is telemetry only\"},\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-16T13:05:00Z\",\"durationMs\":90000}' >> \"$F\"\nprintf '%s\\n' '{\"type\":\"event\",\"event\":\"dashboard_generated\",\"iteration\":1,\"timestamp\":\"2026-07-16T13:05:30Z\"}' >> \"$F\"\necho \"appended; line count:\"; wc -l < \"$F\"","time":