: \"Mobbin design MCP is remote Streamable HTTP at https://api.mobbin.com/mcp; no local process; mutatesWorkspace:false holds.\", \"run\": 1, \"source\": \"server.json; mcp.json\"},\n    {\"id\": \"f-server-repo-thin\", \"text\": \"mobbin-mcp-server repo is metadata-only (README, mcp.json, server.json, rules/, .cursor-plugin/).\", \"run\": 1, \"source\": \"github.com/mobbin/mobbin-mcp-server\"},\n    {\"id\": \"f-two-servers\", \"text\": \"TWO distinct Mobbin MCPs: api.mobbin.com/mcp (design refs, com.mobbin/mobbin) vs docs.mobbin.com/mcp (Mintlify docs, 'Mobbin Docs'). Do NOT conflate.\", \"run\": 2, \"source\": \"server.json; docs.mobbin.com/mcp\"},\n    {\"id\": \"f-search-screens\", \"text\": \"Design MCP tool = search_screens (query/platform/limit/deep) returns inline image content blocks + metadata.\", \"run\": 2, \"source\": \"mobbin-search SKILL.md\"},\n    {\"id\": \"f-no-client-key\", \"text\": \"All documented client configs are url-only; no static API key/headers/OAuth field present.\", \"run\": 2, \"source\": \"mcp.json; skills README\", \"confidence\": \"inferred\"},\n    {\"id\": \"f-images-inline\", \"text\": \"MCP returns images inline; mobbin-search visually inspects them; natural sk-design pairing surface.\", \"run\": 1, \"source\": \"mobbin/skills\"},\n    {\"id\": \"f-gating-unknown\", \"text\": \"Free-vs-Pro plan gating is undocumented in all fetched sources.\", \"run\": 2, \"source\": \"absence-of-evidence\", \"confidence\": \"unknown\"},\n    {\"id\": \"f-docs-mcp-secondary\", \"text\": \"docs.mobbin.com/mcp is a clean read-only docs-search surface (secondary candidate, out of primary mcp-mobbin scope).\", \"run\": 2, \"source\": \"docs.mobbin.com/mcp\"}\n  ],\n  \"ruledOutDirections\": [\n    {\"approach\": \"Read auth/plan-gating/tool-list from server repo README\", \"reason\": \"READMEs omit them\", \"evidence\": \"github.com/mobbin/mobbin-mcp-server\", \"run\": 1},\n    {\"approach\": \"Local stdio process install (npx/node command)\", \"reason\": \"Server is remote streamable-http; url-only config\", \"evidence\": \"mcp.json\", \"run\": 1},\n    {\"approach\": \"Target docs.mobbin.com/mcp as the design server\", \"reason\": \"It is a separate Mintlify docs-search server; design refs at api.mobbin.com/mcp\", \"evidence\": \"server.json; docs.mobbin.com/mcp\", \"run\": 2}\n  ],\n  \"rejectedPatterns\": [],\n  \"rejectedPatternIndex\": [],\n  \"suppressedCandidates\": [],\n  \"promotedIdeas\": []\n}\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/mcp-tooling/010-mcp-mobbin/001-research/research/lineages/glm/findings-registry.json"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/mcp-tooling/010-mcp-mobbin/001-research/research/lineages/glm/findings-registry.json","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/mcp-tooling/010-mcp-mobbin/001-research/research/lineages/glm/findings-registry.json","time":{"start":1784200182526,"end":1784200182530}},"id":"prt_f6a9e3afc001Wzwzptm8BkgU0z","sessionID":"ses_0956a1d5cffeqD3bmKvYqpd743","messageID":"msg_f6a9def13001eqnU2T1D2U002q"}}
